{
  "info": {
    "name": "DeliveryApp - Todos los Endpoints",
    "description": "Coleccion de referencia con TODOS los endpoints del proyecto (41 en total), organizada en carpetas por modulo en el mismo orden de dependencias que usa la API: auth, usuarios, inventario, menu (categorias y platillos), recetas, repartidores, pedidos-mesa, pedidos-delivery, caja y rentabilidad.\n\nA diferencia de la coleccion 'DeliveryApp.postman_collection.json' (que solo demuestra el flujo de negocio principal), esta coleccion recorre cada endpoint disponible al menos una vez, incluyendo las operaciones CRUD completas (crear, listar, obtener por ID, actualizar y eliminar) donde existen.\n\nSe puede ejecutar completa con 'Run Collection': cada carpeta encadena con la siguiente mediante variables (IDs creados). Los nombres/emails usan {{$timestamp}} para que la coleccion sea repetible sin chocar por valores unicos duplicados.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000/api" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "fecha", "value": "" },
    { "key": "usuarioTempId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "ingredienteId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "ingredienteTempId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "categoriaId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "categoriaTempId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "platilloId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "platilloTempId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "repartidorId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "pedidoMesaId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "numeroMesaB", "value": "" },
    { "key": "pedidoDeliveryId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01. Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Registrar usuario público (rol mesero por defecto)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Usuario Demo\",\n  \"email\": \"demo{{$timestamp}}@delivery.com\",\n  \"password\": \"demo1234\",\n  \"telefono\": \"+503 7000-0000\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": ["pm.test('registro 201', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]));"]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (admin) - obtiene token para el resto de la colección",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@delivery.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('login 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.access_token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('fecha', new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener perfil del usuario autenticado",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/profile", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "profile"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('profile 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"] }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
